d":"deb07b3911dd7387141fe48739316c54471d0add","tid":891774,"uid":112436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I hope my kids grow up to learn to answer the call to serve wherever it comes, not necessarily in the military but whatever profession, whatever community need, whatever religious need,&quot; said Jennie Taylor. &quot;I hope they know that in our family, we help. In our family, we do what we can. If it&rsquo;s something we can do, and the call comes to serve, we say yes.&rdquo; -Brent Taylor"},{"pid":"64f0e5d062dea10256048fa22fdbbb49e8a54230","tid":891774,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"阿富汗部隊一名成員忽然襲擊美軍，造成一死一傷，殺手當場斃命。<br />\n<br />\n特登派人去殺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真正headhunt"}]}